Package com.saggezza.jtracker.track

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GenericTracker
    GenericTracker Interface The generic tracker interface is used to track whatever unstructured data in tabular form.
    PayloadMap
    PayloadMap interface The PayloadMap is used to store all the parameters and configurations that are used to send data via the HTTP GET request.
    PlowContractor.Function<T>
    Slight work-around due to lack of lambda functions.
    Tracker
    Tracker Interface The tracker interface contains all usable tracking commands that are implemented in the TrackerC class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PayloadMapC
    PayloadMapC implements the PayloadMap interface The PayloadMap is used to store all the parameters and configurations that are used to send data via the HTTP GET request.
    PlowContractor<T>
    Contractor Class The contractor class is used to create a standard list of assertions that abide by the saggezza conventions.
    TrackerC
    TrackerC is the implementing class for the Tracker interface.
    Version
    The version class is used for documentation purposes.
